{"tid":1810510,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"點開台灣銀行戶口","createTime":"2020-01-04T02:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T01:54:18.000Z","uid":144372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"893c2e4cdc7492f3465a9c3579e16a32fe84497a","tid":1810510,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:50:26.000Z","msg":"旅客身份，喺台灣有親戚<br />\n開唔開到戶口<br />\n網上啲資訊好亂有啲話得有啲話唔得<br />\n有啲話要地址證明但同一間銀行第二個分行又唔使<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打分享經驗"},{"pid":"3071c5a2cf14e07e2f56cabcc6dc51714141b45b","tid":1810510,"uid":126053,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:52:08.000Z","msg":"開到<br />\n<br />\n首先要香港出世<br />\n<br />\n拎張台證去移民署<br />\n<br />\n拎個統一證號<br />\n<br />\n再去銀行 （ 只限官股行庫）"},{"pid":"af72c9a00b2b0f3db2120f7a2cfce64e6e9f5df2","tid":1810510,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:53:15.000Z","msg":"地址證明 就要睇咩銀行<br />\n<br />\n我開頭揾富邦 國泰 全部都要地址證明"},{"pid":"8713e7f16542ad26e63e6e929340e6f7e2ba6e23","tid":1810510,"uid":326426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"上海商業銀行😂"},{"pid":"30d2e8a697cf53a49303f49330bc901d53da0d73","tid":1810510,"uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3071c5a2cf14e07e2f56cabcc6dc51714141b45b","tid":1810510,"uid":126053,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:52:08.000Z","msg":"開到<br />\n<br />\n首先要香港出世<br />\n<br />\n拎張台證去移民署<br />\n<br />\n拎個統一證號<br />\n<br />\n再去銀行 （ 只限官股行庫）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"唔同支那出世會走嚟呢度問咩"},{"pid":"5cbcdeb01124fe401f704f40f7736474809078b9","tid":1810510,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"30d2e8a697cf53a49303f49330bc901d53da0d73","tid":1810510,"uid":144372,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3071c5a2cf14e07e2f56cabcc6dc51714141b45b","tid":1810510,"uid":126053,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:52:08.000Z","msg":"開到<br />\n<br />\n首先要香港出世<br />\n<br />\n拎張台證去移民署<br />\n<br />\n拎個統一證號<br />\n<br />\n再去銀行 （ 只限官股行庫）"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:05:17.000Z","msg":"唔同支那出世會走嚟呢度問咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:06:01.000Z","msg":"支那出世 冇得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f311bdce7915488f7af115cd38da6b1ab4b1db","tid":1810510,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:11:47.000Z","msg":"點解要在台灣開戶？"},{"pid":"3146d13fbf93567fe258e0705a3b528b689c298b","tid":1810510,"uid":337026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"早幾年係郵局開，只要統一證號，護照同印章，開完一個禮拜後會打電話叫你翻去拎簿仔同提款卡，唔知依家有冇變。"},{"pid":"aba1d61f875ef7a992510982e58adf4d754e365c","tid":1810510,"uid":126053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3146d13fbf93567fe258e0705a3b528b689c298b","tid":1810510,"uid":337026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:19:24.000Z","msg":"早幾年係郵局開，只要統一證號，護照同印章，開完一個禮拜後會打電話叫你翻去拎簿仔同提款卡，唔知依家有冇變。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:31:19.000Z","msg":"郵局太慢了<br />\n同埋好似做唔到電滙"},{"pid":"d642103fb51f70da29048926e20ddb76e141d8ce","tid":1810510,"uid":126053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"66f311bdce7915488f7af115cd38da6b1ab4b1db","tid":1810510,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:11:47.000Z","msg":"點解要在台灣開戶？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T03:31:55.000Z","msg":"最低門檻 離岸戶口"},{"pid":"9e4a9d3770fbe6f194e5339a8c56488b097ae4a1","tid":1810510,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8713e7f16542ad26e63e6e929340e6f7e2ba6e23","tid":1810510,"uid":326426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T02:53:49.000Z","msg":"上海商業銀行😂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T04:10:41.000Z","msg":"Fact checked?"},{"pid":"114b7276858e403da28fa47cd5230bfb741804f7","tid":1810510,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af72c9a00b2b0f3db2120f7a2cf